<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qtnfc-index.xml">Qt NFC</db:link> C++ API enables an application to access NFC Forum Tags.</db:para>
<db:para>To use the C++ library in your application, add the following configuration option to your <db:code>.pro</db:code> file:</db:para>
<db:programlisting language="cpp">QT += nfc
</db:programlisting>
